data <- read.csv('data\\run1_data.csv')
head(data)
data <- data %>% ungroup() %>% bind_cols(s_num = group_indices(., subjectID))


for (s in 1:10){
  subj_data <- data %>% filter(s_num == s)
  subj_data <- clean_subj_data(subj_data)
  plot_subj_basic(subj_data)  
}
